import React from 'react';
import { Box, Container, Typography, Grid, Paper, IconButton, Link } from '@mui/material';
import { Email, Phone, LinkedIn, LocationOn } from '@mui/icons-material';
import { motion } from 'framer-motion';

const Contact: React.FC = () => {
  return (
    <Box
      id="contact"
      sx={{
        py: 8,
        backgroundColor: '#fff',
      }}
    >
      <Container>
        <motion.div
          initial={{ opacity: 0 }}
          whileInView={{ opacity: 1 }}
          viewport={{ once: true }}
          transition={{ duration: 1 }}
        >
          <Typography variant="h3" component="h2" gutterBottom align="center" color="primary">
            Contact Me
          </Typography>

          <Grid container spacing={4} sx={{ mt: 2 }} justifyContent="center">
            <Grid item xs={12} md={8}>
              <Paper elevation={3} sx={{ p: 4 }}>
                <Grid container spacing={3}>
                  <Grid item xs={12} sm={6}>
                    <Box sx={{ display: 'flex', alignItems: 'center', mb: 2 }}>
                      <IconButton color="primary" sx={{ mr: 2 }}>
                        <Email />
                      </IconButton>
                      <Box>
                        <Typography variant="h6">Email</Typography>
                        <Link href="mailto:mprabhat1607@gmail.com" color="primary" underline="hover">
                          mprabhat1607@gmail.com
                        </Link>
                      </Box>
                    </Box>
                  </Grid>

                  <Grid item xs={12} sm={6}>
                    <Box sx={{ display: 'flex', alignItems: 'center', mb: 2 }}>
                      <IconButton color="primary" sx={{ mr: 2 }}>
                        <Phone />
                      </IconButton>
                      <Box>
                        <Typography variant="h6">Phone</Typography>
                        <Link href="tel:+917990676099" color="primary" underline="hover">
                          +91 7990676099
                        </Link>
                      </Box>
                    </Box>
                  </Grid>

                  <Grid item xs={12} sm={6}>
                    <Box sx={{ display: 'flex', alignItems: 'center', mb: 2 }}>
                      <IconButton color="primary" sx={{ mr: 2 }}>
                        <LinkedIn />
                      </IconButton>
                      <Box>
                        <Typography variant="h6">LinkedIn</Typography>
                        <Link 
                          href="https://linkedin.com/in/Prabhat" 
                          target="_blank" 
                          rel="noopener noreferrer"
                          color="primary"
                          underline="hover"
                        >
                          Prabhat/linkedin
                        </Link>
                      </Box>
                    </Box>
                  </Grid>

                  <Grid item xs={12} sm={6}>
                    <Box sx={{ display: 'flex', alignItems: 'center', mb: 2 }}>
                      <IconButton color="primary" sx={{ mr: 2 }}>
                        <LocationOn />
                      </IconButton>
                      <Box>
                        <Typography variant="h6">Location</Typography>
                        <Typography color="textSecondary">
                          Pune, Maharashtra
                        </Typography>
                      </Box>
                    </Box>
                  </Grid>
                </Grid>
              </Paper>
            </Grid>
          </Grid>

          <Box sx={{ mt: 6, textAlign: 'center' }}>
            <Typography variant="body1" color="textSecondary">
              Â© {new Date().getFullYear()} Prabhat Mishra. All rights reserved.
            </Typography>
          </Box>
        </motion.div>
      </Container>
    </Box>
  );
};

export default Contact;
